{"tid":1135720,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【爭議瞬間】利物浦禁區內手球竟被忽略？","createTime":"2019-05-02T13:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T16:35:56.000Z","uid":147522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6750c16738cadd62be4e63a064b6dd291313a2c","tid":1135720,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"　　在巴塞與利物浦歐聯大戰的上半場比賽中出現了爭議一幕，利物浦後衛馬迪普（J.Matip）在禁區內有手球嫌疑，不過球證沒有做判罰。<br />\n<br />\n　　上半場第14分鐘，美斯（L.Messi）在禁區內持球，而馬迪普在防守過程中，伸手碰到皮球阻擋了球的前進。美斯馬上轉身向球證示意球打在手上，但荷蘭球證庫伊佩爾斯沒有做任何判罰，也沒有確認VAR。<br />\n<br />\n　　西班牙媒體方面都認為此球應判罰。《阿斯報》引用球證專家伊圖拉德-干沙利斯的觀點表示，這個動作是用手掌握了皮球，球甚至在他的拍擊下轉了一圈，這是個明顯的12碼。<br />\n<br />\n　　《馬卡報》的球證專家安杜哈爾也表示，這看起來像個12碼，馬迪普的手並不是在自然的位置。"},{"pid":"299e5c3b942999e89fb8c190a0b4cb0c9061e6f0","tid":1135720,"uid":213607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"得巴塞係勁到踢贏四隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9fa1fa3788a021839759fb07b04e4518094a34","tid":1135720,"uid":25831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f779940901202013981303c47ed040cb65f3dc2","tid":1135720,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"前足掂波吹啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個二個都唔撚sick ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcde726e35b5013cc607aa47c1460ae8e7030d2","tid":1135720,"uid":3194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"4隻腳都有得吹?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}